              <title>Self-paced learning with online materials</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/270</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/270</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[Students often progress at different speeds, for example where theoretical concepts are concerned, but contact time with teachers is limited – especially when students are attending college on a day-release basis, as on this course.

Here, the leader of a course on gas services installation and maintenance assembled VLE resources – such as notes and handouts, diagrams, photographs, and videos – to allow students to reinforce difficult concepts at their own pace and then follow them up in class. The VLE also delivers practice assessments and mock exams.

[Brian Keating]]]></description>
